---
<div class="section-divider"></div>
<section id="interests">
  <div style="padding-left: 2rem;">
    <p class="section-label fade-in">Interests & Beyond</p>
    <h2 class="section-title fade-in fade-in-delay-1">Life Outside<br /><em>the Classroom</em></h2>
    <span class="gold-line fade-in fade-in-delay-2"></span>
  </div>
  <div class="interests-grid">
    <div class="interest-card card fade-in fade-in-delay-2">
      <div class="interest-icon">&#9917;</div>
      <h3>Arsenal FC</h3>
      <p>
        A committed Gooner through the highs and the near-misses. Following the
        Premier League is part ritual, part obsession — and a reminder that passion
        and patience go hand in hand.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="interest-card card fade-in fade-in-delay-3">
      <div class="interest-icon">&#9992;</div>
      <h3>Travel</h3>
      <p>
        I've been fortunate to explore widely — Africa, Mexico, Costa Rica, Honduras,
        Belize, Alaska, countless U.S. national parks, and many trips to Los Angeles.
        Every destination has sharpened how I see the world.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="interest-card card fade-in fade-in-delay-4">
      <div class="interest-icon">&#127754;</div>
      <h3>Sea Isle City</h3>
      <p>
        Summers on the Jersey Shore with family are a constant. Sea Isle City is where
        I recharge — the kind of place that slows everything down in the best possible way.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="interest-card card fade-in fade-in-delay-2">
      <div class="interest-icon">&#128167;</div>
      <h3>Milner Pressure Washing</h3>
      <p>
        Co-owner and operator of a small business I run with my cousin. We offer
        pressure washing services to local residents throughout the summer — my first
        real lesson in hustle, customer service, and entrepreneurship.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="looking-ahead fade-in">
    <div class="card" style="border-color: rgba(201,168,76,0.2); background: rgba(201,168,76,0.04);">
      <p class="section-label">Looking Ahead</p>
      <p class="ahead-text">
        I'm in the process of identifying colleges and programs that will best prepare
        me for a career in law. I'm looking for environments that challenge me academically,
        offer strong pre-law pathways, and push me to grow as a thinker and leader.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .interests-grid {
    display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem; margin-top: 3rem; margin-bottom: 3rem; padding-left: 2rem;
  }
  .interest-card { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem; }
  .interest-icon { font-size: 1.8rem; color: var(--gold); }
  .interest-card h3 {
    font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
    font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 400; color: var(--cream);
  }
  .interest-card p { font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--text-muted); }
  .looking-ahead { margin-top: 1rem; padding-left: 2rem; }
  .ahead-text { font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.9; color: rgba(245,240,232,0.75); }
  @media (max-width: 768px) { .interests-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
</style>
